ol because it leaves my skin feeling smooth, and with the green tea base, it is not harsh or irritating on my sensitive skin.</li>\r\n	<li>Warming Green Tea Scrub - The warmth and grittiness of this scrub on my skin gives me a true clean and refreshing feeling. I love the way this product exfoliates deep into my skin, shedding the dead and promoting the new, and how it really cleans out my pores making them less noticeable and dirt free!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Favorite Service(s) at Lébo:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Laser Hair Removal - I love how this service decreases the amount of time to get ready in the morning, and leaves you worry free of any dark, embarrassing or unwanted hair!</li>\r\n	<li>Microdermabrasion - I like Microdermabrasion because it exfoliates the dead skin, promoting new, and causes collagen to smooth fine lines and even out the texture of your skin, leaving you with a healthy glow!</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3323,353,'_staff_members_21_favorites','field_558af87f8229c'),(3324,353,'staff_members_21_credentials',''),(3325,353,'_staff_members_21_credentials','field_558b07a881d3b'),(3326,353,'staff_members_22_favorites','<strong>Favorite Skin Care Products at Lébo:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Warming Green Tea Scrub - This scrub instantly reduced the size of my enlarged pores! Not only that, it leaves my skin looking refreshed and feeling incredibly smooth.</li>\r\n	<li>Retinol Serum - This should be a staple in everyone’s regimen! The retinol with green tea has transformed my dull and tired looking skin into a brighter and more youthful textured skin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Favorite Service(s) at Lébo:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Chemical Peels - They have been incredible in lightening my dark spots and improving my skins overall radiance!</li>\r\n	<li>Laser Hair Removal - I don’t need to own a razor any longer!</li>\r\n</ul>'),(3327,353,'_staff_members_22_favorites','field_558af87f8229c'),(3328,353,'staff_members_22_credentials',''),(3329,353,'_staff_members_22