om/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2025',0,'testimonial','',0),(2026,1,'2015-07-01 18:51:52','2015-07-01 18:51:52','<div>Lébo is where I go for all my skin care needs.  From the quality products that give results to the treatments that help me feel and look my personal best.  The staff at Lébo is knowledgeable and friendly.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I trust that I am getting the care I need within my budget.  I receive compliments about my skin and know it is due to the skin care regimen I have been on for the last several years.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you Lebo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Cindy','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonials-by-cindy','','','2015-07-01 19:16:29','2015-07-01 19:16:29','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2026',0,'testimonial','',0),(2027,1,'2015-07-01 18:52:18','2015-07-01 18:52:18','<div>When I first came to Dana my face had lots of melia.  Thanks to Lebo, I now get so many compliments on my complexion.  I have been told I look young for my age of 68 – almost 69.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thanks Lébo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Donna','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-donna','','','2015-07-01 19:16:28','2015-07-01 19:16:28','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2027',0,'testimonial','',0),(2028,1,'2015-07-01 18:53:47','2015-07-01 18:53:47','<div>I appreciate how thorough Dana is with my treatments.  She really takes the time to explain what she is doing and why.  I feel like I get the benefits of a skin treatment and a spa facial all in one.  Well worth the money!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tracey','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-tracey','','','2015-07-01 19:16:11','2015-07-01 19:16:11','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2028',0,'testimonial','',0),(2029,1,'2015-07-01 18:54:15','2015-07-01 18:54:15','<div>Morgan is an exceptional esthetician with the personal desire to share her knowledge of skin care with each of her clients on a personal level.  Her ability to really listen and understand the client is superlative.  She has an unparalleled level of professionalism and always considers what is in the client’s best interest.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Morgan’s conviction and dedication to provide each client with beautiful skin shines through in her enthusiasm.’</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Brandy','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-brandy','','','2015-07-01 19:16:05','2015-07-01 19:16:05','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2029',0,'testimonial','',0),(2030,1,'2015-07-01 18:57:47','2015-07-01 18:57:47','<div>I am always relaxed for appointments knowing that Lébo is dedicated to beautiful skin.  Their state of the art medical equipment, experienced physicians and estheticians, and professional skin care line offer the quality of services of skin deserves.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The knowledgeable staff exceeds all expectations and is dedicated to personalized service.  Lébo has brought out my inner beauty by restoring my outer beauty with beautiful skin.  It feels wonderful to feel beautiful.’</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Allison','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-allison','','','2015-07-01 19:17:12','2015-07-01 19:17:12','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2030',0,'testimonial','',0),(2031,1,'2015-07-01 19:03:15','2015-07-01 19:03:15','<div>Having been a lifelong sun worshipper, Hillary, with understanding and compassion, re-educated me and has done a wonderful job repairing damage!  She makes me feel comfortable in my skin.  I love how Lébo keeps up with all the latest treatments and can tell me which is best for me.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Jane C.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-jane-c','','','2015-07-01 19:15:52','2015-07-01 19:15:52','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2031',0,'testimonial','',0),(2032,1,'2015-07-01 19:03:48','2015-07-01 19:03:48','<div>I have been coming to Lébo for a couple of years and have only had wonderful experiences with all my procedures.  From the front desk always being warm and friendly to the estheticians continuously listening to your wants and needs and always fulfilling your expectations 100%!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Lébo is like my second family!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Christine H.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-christine-h','','','2015-07-01 19:15:43','2015-07-01 19:15:43','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2032',0,'testimonial','',0),(2033,1,'2015-07-01 19:04:26','2015-07-01 19:04:26','<div>Lebo is such a positive place to come in and have treatments done.  Everyone is so kind and positive. The staff really knows their craft and are very talented at what they do every day.  I highly recommend services at Lebo to anyone in need of freshening up!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Natalie G.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-natalie-g','','','2015-07-01 19:15:36','2015-07-01 19:15:36','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2033',0,'testimonial','',0),(2034,1,'2015-07-01 19:04:59','2015-07-01 19:04:59','<div>I was having lunch in Washington D.C. with my daughter back in 2006 when another customer had referred us as sisters.  For me at first, I thought how grown up she has become until I say her reaction.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>What?  She is my mom!!! That’s Lebo Skin Care I said to my daughter.  I then sang Lebo-Acopello style all the way home.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Violet P.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-violet-p','','','2015-07-01 19:15:30','2015-07-01 19:15:30','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2034',0,'testimonial','',0),(2035,1,'2015-07-01 19:06:02','2015-07-01 19:06:02','<div>I was with my husband out to eat at a local club here in York, PA when another person patron looked at him as we were entering and stated, “Is this your daughter” and the look on my husband’s face was enough to smile inside.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Then later I said to him, “Lébo has this effect on people” J</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Paula','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-paula','','','2015-07-01 19:14:52','2015-07-01 19:14:52','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2035',0,'testimonial','',0),(2036,1,'2015-07-01 19:06:35','2015-07-01 19:06:35','<div>Lébo has been my saving grace over the years.  The staff is always working hard to help you help yourself.  The best part – Lebo treats you like family and cares about your services.  Hey, as long as I can get compliments like “you do not look …”!! – I’ll take it any price!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thanks to Lébo for being top notch!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Betty Ann','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-betty-ann','','','2015-07-01 19:14:27','2015-07-01 19:14:27','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2036',0,'testimonial','',0),(2037,1,'2015-07-01 19:07:22','2015-07-01 19:07:22','<div>Having been a client at Lébo Skin Care Center since the beginning, I can truly attest that this is a “center of excellence.”  Hillary and Heather have devoted themselves to ensure that exceptional service is the key priority and the services that are offered are state of art, and truly beneficial to their clients.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Their understanding of each client as an individual enhances the ability to provide the client with an outstanding experience with outstanding results.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I, personally, am often complimented on the quality of my skin – which I truly attribute to Lebo and their product line.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you for 10 plus years of outstanding service!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Marci R.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-marci-r','','','2015-07-01 19:14:20','2015-07-01 19:14:20','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2037',0,'testimonial','',0),(2038,1,'2015-07-01 19:07:52','2015-07-01 19:07:52','<div>I love the way my skin looks! I had sun damage, sun spots and intermittent hormonal acne. Thanks to Lebo Skin Care Center, my skin is clear and smooth. Everyone is so friendly and knowledgeable; it is a joy to come here!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','JoAnn C.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-joann-c','','','2015-07-01 19:14:13','2015-07-01 19:14:13','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2038',0,'testimonial','',0),(2039,1,'2015-07-01 19:08:31','2015-07-01 19:08:31','<div>I cannot thank Lebo Skin Care Center enough as they helped me prepare for my class reunion! I had lost a lot of weight in the past months and it really showed in my face. I even brought a friend so I could show her how much I love the Lebo!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>After visiting with Lebo, I had a makeover. I feel great and cannot thank you all enough for the great experiences that I have at each visit.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Sarah L.','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-sarah-l','','','2015-07-01 19:14:06','2015-07-01 19:14:06','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2039',0,'testimonial','',0),(2040,1,'2015-07-01 19:09:01','2015-07-01 19:09:01','<div>I want to thank Lebo Skin Care Center for changing my life. As dramatic as that sounds, it is probably an</div>\r\n<div>understatement. I avoided mirrors as much as I could because what it reflected wasn’t what I wanted to see. It made me sad and I had given up and decided that my “pretty” days were over and it was time to accept it. And then, one magical day – I learned of the Lebo Skin Care Center. They looked at my face and saw what is was and what could be again. They would accept no less. The staff at Lebo have a wonderful blend of artistic, skill, technical know-how and compassion. They are masters in their field.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Before Lebo Skin Care Center, I didn’t think I would ever smile into a mirror again…and now, I catch myself doing it all the time! What you have given me back spills over in my life. I am a happier person, I</div>\r\n<div>take better care of myself and enjoy life more. Vanity truly is the ultimate of self-respect, and I deserve</div>\r\n<div>it! Thank you, Thank you, Thank you. I am a client for life!\"</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Alexis','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonial-by-alexis','','','2015-07-01 19:13:57','2015-07-01 19:13:57','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2040',0,'testimonial','',0),(2041,1,'2015-07-01 19:09:54','2015-07-01 19:09:54','<div>Awesome!  Very professional and thorough with explaining expectations…Excellent Results!  I am very pleased!  Thank you so much Lebo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Diane','','publish','closed','closed','','diane','','','2015-07-01 19:13:48','2015-07-01 19:13:48','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2041',0,'testimonial','',0),(2042,1,'2015-07-01 19:16:11','2015-07-01 19:16:11','<div>I am always relaxed for appointments knowing that Lébo is dedicated to beautiful skin.  Their state of the art medical equipment, experienced physicians and estheticians, and professional skin care line offer the quality of services of skin deserves.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>The knowledgeable staff exceeds all expectations and is dedicated to personalized service.  Lébo has brought out my inner beauty by restoring my outer beauty with beautiful skin.  It feels wonderful to feel beautiful.’</div>\n&nbsp;','Allison','','inherit','open','open','','2030-autosave-v1','','','2015-07-01 19:16:11','2015-07-01 19:16:11','',2030,'http://www.gavin