nadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2058',0,'testimonial','',0),(2059,1,'2015-07-02 17:29:50','2015-07-02 17:29:50','<div>Botox in my forehead has also been a great help as I had fine wrinkles across my forehead.  Botox has made my forehead smooth.  No wrinkles!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Kristi','','publish','closed','closed','','kristi','','','2015-07-02 17:30:30','2015-07-02 17:30:30','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2059',0,'testimonial','',0),(2060,1,'2015-07-02 17:30:53','2015-07-02 17:30:53','<div>I’ve always thought I looked young for my age, but in the last few years I’ve noticed more and deeper lines marring my forehead.  I never considered BOTOX until I joined a networking group and I’ve always thought I looked young for my age, but in the last few years I’ve noticed more and deeper lines marring my forehead.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I never considered BOTOX until I joined a networking group and met one of the owners of Lébo Skin Care Center.  She told me what BOTOX could do for me so I decided to give it a try.  I’m very pleased with the results.  I no longer have deep furrows on my forehead and I feel I look young again.  Thank you, Lébo Skin Care Center.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tara H.','','publish','closed','closed','','tara-h','','','2015-07-02 17:30:53','2015-07-02 17:30:53','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2060',0,'testimonial','',0),(2061,1,'2015-07-02 17:31:12','2015-07-02 17:31:12','<div>Thanks to Botox I have no lines or wrinkles on my forehead….I LOVE IT!!!!  I still look natural, just a nice overall appearance!!! J  Thank you Botox and Lebo Skin Care Center…my skin loves you!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tara B.','','publish','closed','closed','','tara-b','','','2015-07-02 17:31:12','2015-07-02 17:31:12','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2061',0,'testimonial','',0),(2062,1,'2015-07-02 17:31:45','2015-07-02 17:31:45','<div>I saw improvement after my first Botox treatment! I love the look that it gives me and can tell immediately when it starts to wear off. I don\'t think I could ever be without it again!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Kacie M.','','publish','closed','closed','','kacie-m','','','2015-07-02 17:31:45','2015-07-02 17:31:45','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2062',0,'testimonial','',0),(2063,1,'2015-07-02 17:32:40','2015-07-02 17:32:40','<div>I just wanted to thank Stacey for my Botox injection. I love the results especially since I was so hesitant after all these years to try it. If I wasn\'t going to my daughter\'s wedding I would have liked for you to have done my nasolabial folds, maybe next time! : ) By the way, I\'ve been checking out the staff, their lips are AWESOME!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Great job!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Lisa Tanner','','publish','closed','closed','','lisa-tanner','','','2015-07-02 17:32:40','2015-07-02 17:32:40','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2063',0,'testimonial','',0),(2064,1,'2015-07-02 17:33:03','2015-07-02 17:33:03','<div>I have had Botox and have always heard the only bad thing about it is that you will get addicted to it and won\'t want to be without it.  Well, I have found that to be true!!  It does exactly what it is supposed to do and that is to relax a muscle so you don\'t show that wrinkle.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I was already forming wrinkles before I got my first treatment of Botox, so along with chemical peels and other skin healthy treatments I have softened those wrinkles along with maintaining them with Botox so that they stay away.  Botox also helps with lifting my sagging brow up too.  I love it!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Sharon B.','','publish','closed','closed','','sharon-b','','','2015-07-02 17:33:03','2015-07-02 17:33:03','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=te