INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2077,1,'2015-07-02 17:38:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-07-02 17:38:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&p=2077',0,'testimonial','',0),(2078,1,'2015-07-02 17:38:52','2015-07-02 17:38:52','The line on my forehead has completely disappeared!  I feel like my forehead is 10 years younger! ☺\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Cathy K.','','publish','closed','closed','','cathy-k','','','2015-07-02 17:38:52','2015-07-02 17:38:52','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2078',0,'testimonial','',0),(2079,1,'2015-07-02 17:39:12','2015-07-02 17:39:12','Stacey was amazing!  I wanted to express how pleased I was with her ability to make me feel comfortable.  Her experience and impeccable customer service was evident and appreciated.  It’s undeniable that she is not only an asset to Lebo Skin Care Center but also to the entire skin care industry.  Stacey sure sets examples for others to emulate and you should feel honored to have her as a part of your stunning “team” of employees.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','M. McClane','','publish','closed','closed','','m-mcclane','','','2015-07-02 17:39:12','2015-07-02 17:39:12','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2079',0,'testimonial','',0),(2080,1,'2015-07-02 17:40:51','2015-07-02 17:40:51','<div>First impressions can be lasting impressions, and thanks to Lebo, I am no longer worried about the first impression my complexion leaves. Lebo and their highly - knowledgeable medical aestheticians have turned my acne-proned skin into a clear complexion.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>After multiple misdiagnosis by other representatives of expensive product lines, and thousands of dollars worth of product that underperformed, Hillary and the Lebo staff quickly diagnosed the problem - suggesting chemical peels and microdermabrasion. They have both helped tremendously in a fairly short time period.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>They offer a wide variety of services and the best pricing in the area. I cannot say enough about the staff and the confidence they have given me. I would, and do, recommend Lebo for anyone looking for safely and effectively improve the appearance of their skin.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Erin Perry-Stine','','publish','closed','closed','','erin-perry-stine','','','2015-07-02 17:40:51','2015-07-02 17:40:51','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2080',0,'testimonial','',0),(2081,1,'2015-07-02 17:41:21','2015-07-02 17:41:21','<div>Throughout my teenage years, and early adulthood, I had the opportunity to be blessed with pesky skin problems. I tried nearly every product that was on the market, hoping to solve my acne problems. Proactive, Clearasil, Neutrogena, Retin-A, Bactrum, the list goes on. I finally contacted Lébo when my doctor informed me that the only product that would clear my skin was Accutane. I was not going to try such a risky and controversial product.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I put my trust in Hillary, followed the daily regimen she directed and underwent a series of chemical peels. The combination of the two drastically improved my skin tone, color and complexion. I couldn\'t be happier with the results I\'ve seen and still continue to see.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I always speak highly of Lébo to anyone who asks and would recommend the people and services to everyone who feels there is no way out.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tyler Hoffman','','publish','closed','closed','','tyler-hoffman','','','2015-07-02 17:41:21','2015-07-02 17:41:21','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2081',0,'testimonial','',0),(2082,1,'2015-07-02 17:41:43','2015-07-02 17:41:43','<div>Lebo Skin Care Center has made a huge difference in my life. I grew up at a time when parents weren’t aware of the damaging effects of the sun. It really took a toll on my face and now chemical peels are Lebo are a blessing! My skin is so much smoother than the first day I walked into Lebo. To top it off, the staff is extremely welcoming and friendly – makes my trip such a great experience!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Kristi Ayres','','publish','closed','closed','','kristi-ayres','','','2015-07-02 17:41:43','2015-07-02 17:41:43','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2082',0,'testimonial','',0),(2083,1,'2015-07-02 17:42:05','2015-07-02 17:42:05','<div>After recently turning 33, I have realized the effect that over exposure of sun has had on my skin, having extreme hyper pigmentation and Melasma.  I was then referred by a friend to Lébo Skin Care Center.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I was nervous and didn’t know what to expect.  For my consult, I had seen Janice, who was very informative and educated in her field of work.  She made me feel at ease by discussing the steps/treatments needed to transform myskin.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>After having two separate treatments of chemical peels, I’m thrilled with the results! My skin is much lighter, smoother and tighter!  My overall skin appearance is amazing!  I have received numerous compliments from family and friends on how well my skin has improved!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Christin B.','','publish','closed','closed','','christin-b','','','2015-07-02 17:42:05','2015-07-02 17:42:05','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2083',0,'testimonial','',0),(2084,1,'2015-07-02 17:42:25','2015-07-02 17:42:25','<em>Since I’ve been going to Lebo for chemical peels my skin’s tone and texture have improved.  The peel has reduced my age appearance, brown spots, reduced my pore size and has softened my lines and wrinkles.  My skin is much firmer.  </em>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The peel stimulates collagen and elasticity and helps with sun damage.  Chemical peels do everything i