,'','publish','closed','closed','','stephanie-2','','','2015-07-02 17:46:10','2015-07-02 17:46:10','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2091',0,'testimonial','',0),(2092,1,'2015-07-02 17:46:46','2015-07-02 17:46:46','<div>I am a 63 yr. old who had the CO2RE done on my face.  After a few days of down time my face was as smooth as my baby granddaughters!  I was recently asked if a co-worker and I were twins, she is 10 yrs. younger!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>NEED I SAY MORE?</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Peg','','publish','closed','closed','','peg','','','2015-07-02 17:46:46','2015-07-02 17:46:46','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2092',0,'testimonial','',0),(2093,1,'2015-07-02 17:47:14','2015-07-02 17:47:14','<div>I’m writing this testimonial to thank Dr. Carter, Delores and Vicki for taking such good care of me during my treatment of the CO2RE.  I had the deep one and the procedure itself for me was mildly uncomfortable, but not unbearable.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>As a matter of fact, I found the next 2 days to be worse than the procedure itself.  Having said that, it wasn’t because I was in pain, it was what I saw in the mirror.  My face slightly swelled and was bright red, then comes the tightness, followed by the shedding of dead skin.  In my opinion, the worse part of the whole thing was the itchiness I got when my skin started healing and not being able to scratch it.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I’m glad I took the week off work to do it, because my face was still red, just a lighter version for about the time.  If you are the type of person who doesn’t care about people noticing then you don’t need to take that much time off.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>It’s been about 2 months since I had the procedure and many have asked how I feel about the results to which I answer, “I’m glad I did it”.  My skin has tightened and some of my larger pores have shrunk.  I also noticed my skin looks brighter due to the shedding of the dead skin.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>If you are considering having the CO2RE treatment, the benefits far exceed the discomfort you will experience.  I would absolutely do it again and hope to put it on my yearly maintenance skin program.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thanks again to the Lébo Staff for their kindness and support during my procedure.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Teresa H.','','publish','closed','closed','','teresa-h','','','2015-07-02 17:47:14','2015-07-02 17:47:14','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2093',0,'testimonial','',0),(2094,1,'2015-07-02 17:47:39','2015-07-02 17:47:39','<div>I had severe ketosis on my face. I was told that the CO2RE treatment would be a good treatment for this problem. I had the CO2RE completed and I am very pleased with the way my face looks and feels. Dr. Carter’s procedure and follow up care were fantastic.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Mark Kuntz','','publish','closed','closed','','mark-kuntz','','','2015-07-02 17:47:39','2015-07-02 17:47:39','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2094',0,'testimonial','',0),(2095,1,'2015-07-02 17:48:06','2015-07-02 17:48:06','<div>The staff at Lebo are very courteous and respectful of my choices.  The results I obtained from Coolsculpting made me feel more confident and comfortable with myself.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Anonymous','','publish','closed','closed','','anonymous-8','','','2015-07-02 17:48:06','2015-07-02 17:48:06','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2095',0,'testimonial','',0),(2096,1,'2015-07-02 17:48:26','2015-07-02 17:48:26','<div>I had the fat removal treatment done at Lebo and the results are great!  I had a baby about 6 months ago and was just not able to lose that stubborn belly fat so I decided to have the Coolsculpting done.  I feel so much better about myself now and I can fit into my jeans again!  I would definitely recommend the treatment to anyone!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Sam G.','','publish','closed','closed','','sam-g','','','2015-07-02 17:48:26','2015-07-02 17:48:26','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2096',0,'testimonial','',0),(2097,1,'2015-07-02 17:48:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-07-02 17:48:31','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&p=2097',0,'testimonial','',0),(2098,1,'2015-07-02 17:48:44','2015-07-02 17:48:44','<div>After I had my three children, I was left with a \"muffin top\". I could not stand the bulge that stuck out of my jeans when I sat down. When I learned about CoolSculpting, I was so excited! I couldn\'t believe there was a non-surgical solution to my problem. I had the treatment done about a year ago. It was so worth it!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>It took about 3 months to notice my results, but it was worth the wait. I love being able to wear my favorite jeans now and know that I have nothing hanging out of the top of it!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','K. Hartley','','publish','closed','closed','','k-hartley','','','2015-07-02 17:48:44','2015-07-02 17:48:44','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2098',0,'testimonial','',0),(2099,1,'2015-07-02 17:49:21','2015-07-02 17:49:21','<div>I had 2 treatments of  coolsculpting on my stomach 18 months ago.  I lost about 2 inches around my stomach area at that time and I can say that I have maintained the same result since that time.  I am very happy with my treatment and I would do it again to rid myself of that stubborn fat area in my lower stomach that seems to appear with age!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Nancy P.','','publish','closed','closed','','nancy-p','','','2015-07-02 17:49:21','2015-07-02 17:49:21','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2099',0,'testimonial','',0),(2100,1,'2015-07-02 17:49:43','2015-07-02 17:49:43','<div>Although working out and eating healthy are both part of my everyday life, I couldn’t seem to get the six pack I was looking to achieve.  I heard on the radio an advertisement for something called Coolsculpting (something that contours the body) at Lebo and decided to call and see what it was about.  After 2 treatments I now have the six pack I’ve been wanting for years!!! Best investment I could EVER make!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you Lebo!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Matt T.','','publish','closed','closed','','matt-t','','','2015-07-02 17:49:43','2015-07-02 17:49:43','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2100',0,'testimonial','',0),(2101,1,'2015-07-02 17:50:06','2015-07-02 17:50:06','<div>I was more than satisfied with my results I received with my treatment of Cool Sculpting! For the most part, I eat a healthy diet and exercise but as I got older my love handles wouldn\'t ever go away to my satisfaction. Cool sculpting was effective, permanent and gave me the definition I was striving for!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','D. Allen','','publish','closed','closed','','d-allen','','','2015-07-02 17:50:06','2015-07-02 17:50:06','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2101',0,'testimonial','',0),(2102,1,'2015-07-02 17:50:51','2015-07-02 17:50:51','<div>While not being familiar with lip injections prior to my lébo experience, I immediately decided this is the place for me.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The doctor paid close attention to what I was looking for and how to achieve it.  The staff is so warm and welcoming, it feels like a family.  Getting the injections done was so much easier than I expected and Stacy did such a wonderful and natural looking job!  I didn’t even bruise at all in the days to follow!  I will be back for sure!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Victoria W.','','publish','closed','closed','','victoria-w','','','20