timonial&#038;p=2128',0,'testimonial','',0),(2129,1,'2015-07-06 13:18:45','2015-07-06 13:18:45','<div>Dear Lebo! I love the Voluma filler!!! It was completely painless, quick with instant results! My face looks thinner, younger and my cheek bones are perfectly shaped now. I feel like a Movie Star! Thank you so much!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','D. Turner','','publish','closed','closed','','d-turner','','','2015-07-06 13:18:45','2015-07-06 13:18:45','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2129',0,'testimonial','',0),(2130,1,'2015-07-06 13:19:39','2015-07-06 13:19:39','<div>I perceive myself as looking five years younger! The pain of injection process was about 2 out of 10. There was some bruising afterward but not enough to keep me from normal daily activities. My skin looks smoother and tighter. I am excited that this treatment will last up to 2 years!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Orbie Fink','','publish','closed','closed','','orbie-fink','','','2015-07-06 13:19:39','2015-07-06 13:19:39','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2130',0,'testimonial','',0),(2131,1,'2015-07-06 13:20:37','2015-07-06 13:20:37','<div>I am a very active woman and don’t feel as old as my age. Over the past few years I feel like my outward appearance has not been matching how I feel on the inside. I had a consultation at Lebo and Voluma was recommended for the result I was looking for. WOW…I am so happy and pleased with the outcome.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I love the lift it gave my cheeks and I can’t believe how natural it looks. It’s funny, when I look in the mirror I think my face looks “pleasant” and I don’t even have to smile! I love it…thanks so much Lebo!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Terrah B.','','publish','closed','closed','','terrah-b','','','2015-07-06 13:20:37','2015-07-06 13:20:37','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2131',0,'testimonial','',0),(2132,1,'2015-07-06 13:21:12','2015-07-06 13:21:12','<div>Voluma was the treatment I was looking for to give my face/checks back the youthful volume it used to have. The best aspect is that it looks very natural; not to mention the treatment only takes about 30 minutes with minimal discomfort and lasts for 2 years!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Crystal D.','','publish','closed','closed','','crystal-d','','','2015-07-06 13:21:12','2015-07-06 13:21:12','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2132',0,'testimonial','',0),(2133,1,'2015-07-06 13:21:43','2015-07-06 13:21:43','<div>Looking at older pictures of myself (more then 15-20 yrs) I noticed I really lost the youthful volume in my cheeks. I was excited to find out there was an easy and safe treatment for correction. Voluma is the first treatment FDA cleared for this.  The treatment itself was very comfortable and only took about 20-30 minutes to complete. There is really no downtime. You can return to work immediately or go out for dinner the same evening.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Terry C.','','publish','closed','closed','','terry-c','','','2015-07-06 13:21:43','2015-07-06 13:21:43','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2133',0,'testimonial','',0),(2134,1,'2015-07-06 13:22:08','2015-07-06 13:22:08','<div>I couldn’t believe the difference voluma made until I was looking through an old photo album. I saw a picture of my husband and I and I can’t believe after having voluma, I now look like I did when I got married, which was 20 years ago. Thank you Lebo and I could not be happier with my results.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Nicole K.','','publish','closed','closed','','nicole-k','','','2015-07-06 13:22:08','2015-07-06 13:22:08','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2134',0,'testimonial','',0),(2135,1,'2015-07-06 13:22:31','2015-07-06 13:22:31','The staff was very informative and told me exactly what was happening the whole time.  Very friendly and happy!  I like to be well informed and I felt I was.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','J. Harter','','publish','closed','closed','','j-harter','','','2015-07-06 13:22:31','2015-07-06 13:22:31','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2135',0,'testimonial','',0),(2136,1,'2015-07-06 13:23:24','2015-07-06 13:23:24','Stacey was so sweet! She was gentle and very informative with the information.  I will be back ☺ Thanks Stacey\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','B. Stewart','','publish','closed','closed','','b-stewart','','','2015-07-06 13:23:24','2015-07-06 13:23:24','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2136',0,'testimonial','',0),(2137,1,'2015-07-06 13:24:06','2015-07-06 13:24:06','These girls were absolutely awesome! So informative, attentive, positive and upbeat! Made my day!!!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','G. Shirey','','publish','closed','closed','','g-shirey','','','2015-07-06 13:24:06','2015-07-06 13:24:06','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2137',0,'testimonial','',0),(2138,1,'2015-07-06 13:26:53','2015-07-06 13:26:53','Stacey was great! She explained everything to me and the procedure was quick.  The results are amazing “subtle enhancement of my natural cheeks!” Looks very natural\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Anonymous','','publish','closed','closed','','anonymous-9','','','2015-07-06 13:26:53','2015-07-06 13:26:53','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2138',0,'testimonial','',0),(2139,1,'2015-07-06 14:09:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-07-06 14:09:18','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&p=2139',0,'testimonial','',0),(2140,1,'2015-07-06 14:47:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-07-06 14:47:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.co