 if a lot of time is spent in the sun, water or if you\'re sweating.\r\n\r\nIt can come in oils, lotions and creams, and people can choose the type of sunscreen based on preference. Sometimes people with oily skin do better with a lotion-based sunscreen, she said.</blockquote>\r\n<a href=\"http://www.ydr.com/local/ci_28379806/sunburn-bug-bites-and-poison-ivy-are-hazards?source=rss\" target=\"_blank\">View the full article here.</a>','YDR: Sunburn, bug bites and poison ivy are hazards to summer skin','','publish','closed','closed','','ydr-sunburn-bug-bites-and-poison-ivy-are-hazards-to-summer-skin','','','2015-07-06 20:36:42','2015-07-06 20:36:42','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=newsworthy&#038;p=2191',0,'newsworthy','',0),(2192,1,'2015-07-06 20:36:32','2015-07-06 20:36:32','','ydr-sunscreen','','inherit','open','open','','ydr-sunscreen','','','2015-07-06 20:36:32','2015-07-06 20:36:32','',2191,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/ydr-sunscreen.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(2193,1,'2015-07-06 20:40:37','2015-07-06 20:40:37','<blockquote>YORK, Pa. – With swimsuit season kicking off, many people may be looking for ways to burn fat, but there’s a new non-surgical procedure that freezes the fat away.<a href=\"http://lebolosethehandles.com/\">CoolSculpting</a> is a noninvasive procedure freezes fat below the skin so it can be flushed out naturally.</blockquote>\r\n<a href=\"http://fox43.com/2015/06/29/new-non-surgical-treatment-freezes-fat-away/\" target=\"_blank\">View the video and full article here.</a>','Fox43 : New non-surgical treatment freezes fat away','','publish','closed','closed','','fox43-new-non-surgical-treatment-freezes-fat-away','','','2015-07-06 20:40:37','2015-07-06 20:40:37','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=newsworthy&#038;p=2193',0,'newsworthy','',0),(2194,1,'2015-07-06 20:40:34','2015-07-06 20:40:34','','lebo-fox43-news','','inherit','open