-07-07 13:51:17','Dana started treating me in Oct 2013.  My hair growth was rampant and even painful within only a few months I have no more ingrown hair and a razor will never touch my face again.  I want to sing Lebo’s praises for all.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Lauren','','publish','closed','closed','','lauren','','','2015-07-07 13:51:17','2015-07-07 13:51:17','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2206',0,'testimonial','',0),(2207,1,'2015-07-07 13:51:38','2015-07-07 13:51:38','Everyone is so welcoming and professional.  I love the results of laser hair removal!  Smooth legs without shaving!  If you’re thinking of trying this…do it!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Amy','','publish','closed','closed','','amy','','','2015-07-07 13:51:38','2015-07-07 13:51:38','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2207',0,'testimonial','',0),(2208,1,'2015-07-07 13:51:59','2015-07-07 13:51:59','Thank goodness for laser hair removal.  It gives me more confidence!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Anonymous','','publish','closed','closed','','anonymous-11','','','2015-07-07 13:51:59','2015-07-07 13:51:59','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2208',0,'testimonial','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2209,1,'2015-07-07 13:52:30','2015-07-07 13:52:30','The laser hair removal has decreased my hair growth by about 90% cutting down on my shaving amount and frequency drastically.  I would never hesitate to have more procedures done or refer my friends and family to Lebo.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','G. Miller','','publish','closed','closed','','g-miller','','','2015-07-07 13:52:30','2015-07-07 13:52:30','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2209',0,'testimonial','',0),(2210,1,'2015-07-07 13:52:53','2015-07-07 13:52:53','Laser hair removal is awesome!  I love not having to shave my skin feels silky smooth all the time! ☺ Thank you Dana for getting me hooked!!!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Stephanie','','publish','closed','closed','','stephanie-3','','','2015-07-07 13:52:53','2015-07-07 13:52:53','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2210',0,'testimonial','',0),(2211,1,'2015-07-07 13:53:13','2015-07-07 13:53:13','My daughter and I wanted to try laser hair removal for a long time but we were scared and unsure.  When we decided to try it we scheduled all our appointments together.  It was a wonderful experience!  The Lebo staff coordinated our appointments and was supportive and answered all our questions.  It was a great mother/daughter endeavor and a positive experience as we shared our individual feelings and thoughts with each other.  Thank you Lebo staff for being a part of this memory my daughter and I shared.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Anonymous','','publish','closed','closed','','anonymous-12','','','2015-07-07 13:53:13','2015-07-07 13:53:13','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2211',0,'testimonial','',0),(2212,1,'2015-07-07 13:53:30','2015-07-07 13:53:30','I’ve battled body hair my whole life.  I’ve grown so tired of shaving, waxing and plucking.  It’s been such a painful body image issue, so I finally said “enough” I’m getting laser hair removal.  I met with Dana, we set up a plan and now I feel extraordinary! When I walk down the aisle this August I will finally feel that my inner beauty matches my outer beauty.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','K. Duncan','','publish','closed','closed','','k-duncan','','','2015-07-07 13:53:30','2015-07-07 13:53:30','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2212',0,'testimonial','',0),(2213,1,'2015-07-07 13:53:50','2015-07-07 13:53:50','I had a wonderful experience at Lebo. The staff was friendly and professional. Appointments were always prompt-no waiting! I love the way my face feels! Thank you Kacie!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','L. Sematoske','','publish','closed','closed','','l-sematoske','','','2015-07-07 13:53:50','2015-07-07 13:53:50','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2213',0,'testimonial','',0),(2214,1,'2015-07-07 14:36:02','2015-07-07 14:36:02','<div>For years I was plucking facial hair with tweezers and it was frustrating and even damaged my skin. Getting laser hair removal on my face was the most positive think I\'ve ever done for my personal health. I always recommend Lebo Skin Care to my friends and family. It\'s important you trust the people you go to for skin care issues. I can\'t wait to get treatment for other areas as well. I don\'t love my unwanted hair but I do love Lebo!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Anonymous','','publish','closed','closed','','anonymous-13','','','2015-07-07 14:36:02','2015-07-07 14:36:02','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2214',0,'testimonial','',0),(2215,1,'2015-07-07 14:37:04','2015-07-07 14:37:04','<div>Laser hair removal is one of the best things I\'ve ever done for myself! If I could have done anything different I would have done it sooner! I had no idea how easy it would be and how reasonable! The expense of a good razor is ridiculous and the time it takes to shave is all over for me YAY!!!!I can\'t even tell you how many times I\'ve made people feel how soft my legs are, no more stubble or razor burn on my bikini line! I LOVE LASER HAIR REMOVAL!!!!!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n&nbsp;','D. Turner','','publish','closed','closed','','d-turner-2','','','2015-07-07 14:38:18','2015-07-07 14:38:18','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2215',0,'testimonial','',0),(2216,1,'2015-07-07 14:38:39','2015-07-07 14:38:39','<div>I had laser hair removal done because I am a body builder.  I am happy with the results and wish I had learned of this treatment a long time ago…would have saved me a lot of time!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tim','','publish','closed','closed','','tim','','','2015-07-07 14:38:39','2015-07-07 14:38:39','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2216',0,'testimonial','',0),(2217,1,'2015-07-07 14:39:29','2015-07-07 14:39:29','<div>I do not like hair anywhere on my body so I frequent Lebo Skin Care Center often.  Thanks to Lebo and laser hair removal I am hair free…very pleased!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Brad','','publish','closed','closed','','brad-2','','','2015-07-07 14:39:29','2015-07-07 14:39:29','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2217',0,'testimonial','',0),(2218,1,'2015-07-07 14:40:14','2015-07-07 14:40:14','<div>Love, Love, Love laser hair removal!!! Hands down my favorite service at Lebo! Best money I ever spent!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Amy','','publish','closed','closed','','amy-2','','','2015-07-07 14:40:14','2015-07-07 14:40:14','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2218',0,'testimonial','',0),(2219,1,'2015-07-07 14:40:34','2015-07-07 14:40:34','<div>I was at the gym one day working out when I realized I had not shaved my under arm.  The embarrassment on that day made me call immediately to schedule a consultation for laser hair removal.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I never want to be caught with hairy under arms again and thanks to Lebo I won’t!  I was so happy with the results of my under arms I have started treatments on my legs!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Bethany','','publish','closed','closed','','bethany','','','2015-07-07 14:40:34','2015-07-07 14:40:34','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2219',0,'testimonial','',0),(2220,1,'2015-07-07 14:41:17','2015-07-07 14:41:17','<div>When I learned of laser hair removal I was a little leery...After having several treatments on my legs and now, not ever having to shave…oh my word, I am a full believer.  I couldn’t be happier with my results!!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I would recommend anyone wanting to be free of razor burn, ingrown hair, or being frustrated with how fast hair grows back after shaving to have laser hair removal.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thanks Lebo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Nicole','','publish','closed','closed','','nicole','','','2015-07-07 14:41:17','2015-07-07 14:41:17','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2220',0,'testimonial','',0),(2221,1,'2015-07-07 14:43:09','2015-07-07 14:43:09','<div>Laser hair removal has been a God-send. Lébo has really helped boost my self-esteem in these areas.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Sandy H.','','publish','closed','closed','','sandy-h','','','2015-07-07 14:43:09','2015-07-07 14:43:09','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2221',0,'testimonial','',0),(2222,1,'2015-07-07 14:43:26','2015-07-07 14:43:26','<div>Several years ago I was tired of shaving, having ingrown hairs and getting rashes from shaving.  So, I came to Lébo and have been incredibly pleased with the laser hair removal treatment!  The staff is kind and helpful as well as the office being clean and beautiful.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank You Lébo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Amy S.','','publish','closed','closed','','amy-s','','','2015-07-07 14:43:26','2015-07-07 14:43:26','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2222',0,'testimonial','',0),(2223,1,'2015-07-07 14:43:42','2015-07-07 14:43:42','<div>I have been pleased with my results with Laser hair removal. I look forward to every visit!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','April','','publish','closed','closed','','april-2','','','2015-07-07 14:43:42','2015-07-07 14:43:42','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2223',0,'testimonial','',0),(2224,1,'2015-07-07 14:44:57','2015-07-07 14:44:57','<div>During my 40’s, I noticed my eyelashes were thinning and becoming brittle and very short.  After</div>\r\n<div>consulting with a Provider at Lebo and learning the true facts about Latisse and its safety, I immediately began using it.  As early as 3 weeks, I was noticing longer lashes when I applied mascara.  As early as 5 weeks, I was noticing longer lashes without mascara.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>By 12 weeks my lashes are now VERY full, VERY long, and uniform.  (I even sneak a little on my eyebrows!).  I’ve now been using Latisse for over 2 years; will turn 50 in December, with the thickest, longest lashes of my life!!!  I supplement my long lashes with black lash tint at Lebo!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Sheri','','publish','closed','closed','','sheri','','','2015-07-07 14:44:57','2015-07-07 14:44:57','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2224',0,'testimonial','',0),(2225,1,'2015-07-07 14:45:50','2015-07-07 14:45:50','<div>All of the staff at Lebo have been wonderful!  My initial consult was scheduled very quickly and everyone is so professional.  I’m having great results with Latisse and have already scheduled a few other procedures.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Cindy Kingsbury','','publish','closed','closed','','cindy-kingsbury','','','2015-07-07 14:45:50','2015-07-07 14:45:50','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2225',0,'testimonial','',0),(2226,1,'2015-07-07 14:46:07','2015-07-07 14:46:07','<div>I really enjoy the results that I get from Latisse.  If I don’t want to wear mascara I don’t have to, as my lashes are long and dark without it. When I do wear mascara, my lashes are much more dramatic.  I LOVE Latisse !!!!!!  It is so easy to use!!!!!!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Shannon Freely','','publish','closed','closed','','shannon-freely','','','2015-07-07 14:46:07','2015-07-07 14:46:07','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2226',0,'testimonial','',0),(2227,1,'2015-07-07 14:47:33','2015-07-07 14:47:33','<div>Latisse has worked wonders for my aging eyelashes!  When I was younger, I had very thick and long lashes but as I aged they became very sparse.  Latisse has helped bring back my youthful fullness to my lashes and I love it!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','C. Trout','','publish','closed','closed','','c-trout','','','2015-07-07 14:47:33','2015-07-07 14:47:33','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2227',0,'testimonial','',0),(2228,1,'2015-07-07 14:48:44','2015-07-07 14:48:44','<div>I have been using Latisse for about a year now and it is THE BEST thing I have ever done (and the easiest)!!  I always get compliments on how pretty my eyelashes are!  They have grown so long and are thicker than ever – it’s also great because I don’t have to put mascara on all of the time!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Judy R.','','publish','closed','closed','','judy-r','','','2015-07-07 14:48:44','2015-07-07 14:48:44','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2228',0,'testimonial','',0),(2229,1,'2015-07-07 14:49:39','2015-07-07 14:49:39','<div>Latisse is a wonder product for producing longer, thicker, and darker eyelashes as promised! I have had no side effects and love that this product enhances my own lashes vs. getting extremely expensive eyelash extensions that cost a small fort