rcles and bags under my eyes, but the eye cream has helped to minimize both conditions!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>The retinol pads are amazing because they aid in sloughing off dead skin as well as any makeup residue that I may have missed, and my fine lines have disappeared!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Nina Jones','','publish','closed','closed','','nina-jones','','','2015-07-07 14:51:34','2015-07-07 14:51:34','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2232',0,'testimonial','',0),(2233,1,'2015-07-07 14:59:14','2015-07-07 14:59:14','<div>I have been using Lebo’s skin care products for about a year now and I have definitely noticed a big change in my skin – it is much smoother and I feel like I have a “glow”!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>My favorite product is the warming green tea scrub – it makes my skin feel so soft and I love how it heats up!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you Lebo!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Beth B.','','publish','closed','closed','','beth-b','','','2015-07-07 14:59:14','2015-07-07 14:59:14','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2233',0,'testimonial','',0),(2234,1,'2015-07-07 14:59:42','2015-07-07 14:59:42','<div>I have struggled with moderate acne breakouts over the years, and tried numerous “Professional strength” acne medications.  Over the past two years, I had been using ProActive acne treatment, but it would never work consistently.  It seemed that soon as I had all of my acne cleared up, my face would dry out and started breaking out even worse.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>About two months ago, I decided to give Lebo Skin Care a try.  Heather at Lebo recommended that I try 10% Benzyl-Peroxide Wash that is sold in there office with no prescription, and no scheduled visit.  I was surprised that while it had a higher concentration of medication than Pro-Active, that one of the main ingredients was actually Aloe.  After using this product for a short amount of time, I noticed my skin was not drying out as much and was clearing up much more quickly.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I am so thankful that I tried this product because it is way more affordable and effective than anything else on the market!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>Thank you Heather and Lebo Skin Care!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Jon Saylor','','publish','closed','closed','','jon-saylor','','','2015-07-07 14:59:42','2015-07-07 14:59:42','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2234',0,'testimonial','',0),(2235,1,'2015-07-07 14:59:58','2015-07-07 14:59:58','<div>I LOVE Nectifirm!!!!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>It is by far one of my favorite products. Within the year I have been using it the lines in my neck, on my chest and under my chin have all faded. If there is any advice I would give to anyone considering it would be start before you ever get the lines but if you already have them you will love it as much as I do. I\'m 44 and Lebo has taken at least eight years off my life!</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>I\'ve also been asked if I have lost weight, I wish that was true, but the Nectifirm has tightened the sides of my neck and appears that I\'m thinner. It also makes my neck feel amazing, very  very soft! I don\'t go a day without my nectifirm. The other great thing is it last a long time you don\'t have to use a lot to get great results!</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Deana Turner','','publish','closed','closed','','deana-turner','','','2015-07-07 14:59:58','2015-07-07 14:59:58','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2235',0,'testimonial','',0),(2236,1,'2015-07-07 15:00:20','2015-07-07 15:00:20','<div>I use the Green Tea Cleanser and also the Green Tea Cream.  They both have helped with my Rosacea.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>When the Green Tea Cream first hits my skin I instantly feel it calm and hydrate my skin.  The Green Tea Cleanser is very gentle too.   It is the type of cleanser that feels good when you have sensitive skin.  I also just started using the Elite SPF 30 as my sunscreen; it is very calming to the skin.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Susan B.','','publish','closed','closed','','susan-b','','','2015-07-07 15:00:20','2015-07-07 15:00:20','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2236',0,'testimonial','',0),(2237,1,'2015-07-07 15:07:39','2015-07-07 15:07:39','<div>Because of the redness in my skin and my skin being fairly sensitive, I have started using the green tea cream every morning and I love it!!!  I’ve also been using the Retinol Pads.  I find that they do help with my breakouts along with giving me a more even skin tone.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Tracey P.','','publish','closed','closed','','tracey-p','','','2015-07-07 15:07:39','2015-07-07 15:07:39','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2237',0,'testimonial','',0),(2238,1,'2015-07-07 15:07:57','2015-07-07 15:07:57','<div>I love the \"Intense Hydration Eye Serum\": The skin around my eyes is thin and vulnerable so I use this product to restore hydration and smooth fine lines to prevent visible signs of aging.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Macey M.','','publish','closed','closed','','macey-m','','','2015-07-07 15:07:57','2015-07-07 15:07:57','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2238',0,'testimonial','',0),(2239,1,'2015-07-07 15:09:31','2015-07-07 15:09:31','<div>I really love the Warming Green Tea Scrub. It exfoliates all of the dead, dry skin and rejuvenates. The warming sensation lets you know it is doing its job, leaving the skin looking new and refreshed with a nice, healthy glow.</div>\r\n&nbsp;','Lana S.','','publish','closed','closed','','lana-s','','','2015-07-07 15:09:31','2015-07-07 15:09:31','',0,'http://www.gavinadvertising.com/leboskincare.com/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=2239',0,'testimonial','',0),(2240,1,'2015-07-07 15:09:47','2015-07-07 15:09:47','<div>Nectifir